WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:03.800
"Fruit"

00:00:04.798 --> 00:00:07.626
(Episode 2: Sprout)

00:00:18.013 --> 00:00:19.433
Slow down your strokes.

00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:21.700
Find the shadows first.

00:00:22.066 --> 00:00:23.600
Don't rush to outline.

00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:28.866
Then... where's the darkest part?

00:00:31.532 --> 00:00:32.732
Look at the light.

00:00:33.400 --> 00:00:35.066
The light comes from here.

00:00:35.066 --> 00:00:37.480
So the shadow should be over here.

00:00:40.979 --> 00:00:44.397
Use the shadows to bring out the edges of the light.

00:00:50.506 --> 00:00:51.400
Here.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:55.266
Let it breathe a little.

00:00:56.066 --> 00:00:57.466
Then start your stroke from here.

00:00:57.879 --> 00:00:59.979
Miss... I can draw it myself.

00:01:08.533 --> 00:01:10.300
Keep the lines crisp.

00:01:10.466 --> 00:01:11.400
Don't let your hand shake.

00:01:13.266 --> 00:01:14.909
Okay, draw another one.

00:01:14.910 --> 00:01:17.666
What? Another one?

00:01:20.366 --> 00:01:22.078
I'll never finish...

00:01:35.966 --> 00:01:37.180
We'll get going.

00:01:37.181 --> 00:01:38.166
I'm almost done.

00:01:38.166 --> 00:01:39.627
Good luck.

00:01:39.628 --> 00:01:41.866
I'm almost done. Really, just a minute.

00:01:41.866 --> 00:01:42.866
- No, got to catch the bus.
- Please.

00:01:42.866 --> 00:01:44.382
- Bye.
- Bye!

00:01:44.383 --> 00:01:46.160
Please stay with me!

00:01:50.727 --> 00:01:53.194
Heartless jerks.

00:01:57.952 --> 00:01:58.984
Almost done?

00:02:00.217 --> 00:02:01.200
You scared me.

00:02:01.600 --> 00:02:04.033
Miss, are you a ghost?

00:02:04.266 --> 00:02:05.633
You walk so silently.

00:02:06.900 --> 00:02:08.066
Just my habit.

00:02:09.300 --> 00:02:10.666
Take a break.

00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:13.500
Thanks.

00:02:24.053 --> 00:02:25.738
It's pretty good.

00:02:27.098 --> 00:02:28.100
Really?

00:02:52.246 --> 00:02:53.451
It's really good.

00:02:53.733 --> 00:02:55.166
Have some too.

00:02:59.914 --> 00:03:00.866
Thanks.

00:03:02.133 --> 00:03:04.866
Hurry up. I want to go home.

00:03:07.832 --> 00:03:11.332
That day, there were a mix of scents in the air.

00:03:11.835 --> 00:03:14.500
Paint, tea,

00:03:14.533 --> 00:03:16.966
maybe the scent of wooden easels.

00:03:17.333 --> 00:03:18.966
In that moment,

00:03:19.300 --> 00:03:22.361
it felt like she was gently caring for me.

00:03:22.896 --> 00:03:24.233
I felt so safe.

00:03:28.366 --> 00:03:30.966
Miss, I was going to leave this part blank,

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:33.200
but I feel like it might be too empty.

00:03:33.200 --> 00:03:34.300
No.

00:03:34.866 --> 00:03:36.366
Your proportions have improved.

00:03:41.766 --> 00:03:43.033
Thanks, Miss.

00:03:55.073 --> 00:03:55.940
Miss.

00:03:56.866 --> 00:03:58.100
Here.

00:03:58.766 --> 00:04:01.430
You look tired. Recharge.

00:04:04.958 --> 00:04:05.999
Thanks.

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:08.000
What is she thinking?

00:04:08.500 --> 00:04:11.800
I want to know if she's in a good mood.

00:04:12.666 --> 00:04:15.233
Miss, you need to take care of yourself.

00:04:21.123 --> 00:04:25.370
Hmm...

00:04:25.371 --> 00:04:27.685
The eraser...

00:04:27.686 --> 00:04:28.753
Here.

00:04:37.433 --> 00:04:41.033
Miss, I heard tomorrow's art class got rescheduled.

00:04:41.034 --> 00:04:42.520
It's going to be study hall.

00:04:45.466 --> 00:04:46.438
Yeah.

00:05:03.286 --> 00:05:05.720
She's become colder than before.

00:05:06.300 --> 00:05:09.300
I wish I could stay by her side longer.